    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Data will only appear in the URL if the custom widget has the following two life cycles too:\r\n\r\n- `getWidgetState(uiState, { helper, searchParameters }): UIState` (merged with existing UIState)\r\n- `getWidgetSearchParameters(searchParameters, { uiState }): SearchParameters` (merged with existing search parameters, usually using helper methods)\r\n\r\n> https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/widgets/create-your-own-widgets/js/?language=js#the-widget-lifecycle-and-api",
